    "As people have adopted LLMs into their daily workflows, it is becoming apparent that having a creative problem-solving mindset and some programming ability allows one to make much more powerful use of the technology.",
    "With some basic coding, one can use an LLM as an agent, which interacts with other applications to complete tasks and automate complex workflows, and not simply as a fancy autocomplete.",
    "As with literacy and numeracy, using AI effectively will be increasingly necessary to compete in the new information economy.",
